# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# wsinsight-model-development — .gitignore
#
# Policy: the repo carries SOURCE only.  Bulk public data, derived training
# artifacts, vendored upstream code, and large model checkpoints are NEVER
# committed.  See data/README.md for how to recreate the data tree locally.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Bulk public data (3 TB+; recreated by following data/README.md) ─────────
# Tissue folders themselves stay tracked (so SOURCES.yaml / README.md commit);
# only the sample-level subdirs (which hold the actual bytes) are ignored.
data/xenium/*/*/
# Census mirrors are date-stamped subfolders right under data/census/:
data/census/*/
# ...but keep top-level data/census/README.md (tracked by default since
# only subdirs are ignored above):

# ── Derived training artifacts (rebuilt by the pipeline) ────────────────────
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/train/
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/val/
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/test/
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/splits/
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/labels/
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/cache/
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/cell_labels_*.csv
# NOTE: label_map.yaml is the canonical int<->name source (see export_tiles.groovy).
# It MUST stay tracked; do not add it to .gitignore.
# Per-tissue train_configs are derived from the pantissue template by
# make_train_config.py. Ignore them all, then re-include the pantissue
# template (canonical source of truth for hyperparams and aug block).
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/train_configs/
!cellvit-training/trainingset/pantissue/train_configs/
!cellvit-training/trainingset/pantissue/train_configs/**
# Resolved (envsubst'd) training configs are always derived, even for pantissue:
cellvit-training/trainingset/*/train_configs/*/.fold_*.resolved.yaml

# ── Trained heads & training logs (not committed; published to HF Hub) ──────
cellvit-training/cellvit/CellViT-plus-plus/logs_local/
cellvit-training/cellvit/CellViT-plus-plus/logs/
cellvit-training/**/checkpoints/
cellvit-training/**/wandb/
cellvit-training/**/*.pth
cellvit-training/**/*.ckpt

# ── Vendored upstream + base weights (re-cloneable; instructions in cellvit/README.md) ──
cellvit-training/cellvit/models/

# ── QuPath projects (large, machine-local; per-image .qpdata is huge) ───────
cellvit-training/qprj/
kurtorank/qprj/
data/qprj/

# ── Pipeline logs & derived audit outputs (machine-local) ──────────────────────
cellvit-training/_logs/
cellvit-training/logs/
cellvit-training/**/audit_outputs/

# ── One-time job outputs (machine-local; re-generatable, never committed) ───
# Per-job logs from reannotate_xenium.py (reannotate/, reannotate_pantissue/).
kurtorank/logs/
# Dated AI-agent orchestration runs (decision_log.jsonl + derived fold configs).
cellvit-training/**/agent_runs/

# ── Quarantined / archived (machine-local, never committed) ────────────────
# Match at any depth (project-root _to_be_deleted/ holds ~170 GB of stale runs).
# Both the underscore and hyphen spellings are honored.
_to_be_deleted/
**/_to_be_deleted/
to-be-deleted/
**/to-be-deleted/

# ── Python build / cache artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
build/
dist/
.eggs/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# ── Conda / virtualenv ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.conda/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ── Editor / IDE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.swp

# ── OS noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── W&B / training run outputs ──────────────────────────────────────────────
wandb/
logs_local/
*.log

# ── Notebook outputs (keep notebooks; strip outputs at commit time) ─────────
*.ipynb_checkpoints
.github/skills/

# ── Temporary files (editor / process scratch, never committed) ─────────────
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.orig
*.rej
*~
nohup.out
core.*
*.pid

# ── Dev scratch (throwaway code/data; use these known-ignored locations) ────
scratch/
sandbox/
**/scratch/
**/sandbox/
*.scratch.*
Untitled*.ipynb
